### Welcome to our Documentation!
This is a constant work in progress as we work to improve the depth of the information available on using the Benedictine Website. If you have a GitHub account or would like to make you, you can feel free to contribute with Pull Requests (adding documentation) or submit Issues on the repo to make requests to be added.

Whooop!
Web Support Team
Benedictine University
